Desert Wind (Strike) [Fire]
Level: Swordsage 4
Prerequisite: One Desert Wind maneuver
Initiation Action: 1 full round
Range: 30ft.
Target: One creature
Duration: Instantaneous

As part of this maneuver, you charge an opponent within range. You must have line of effect to your target.  You fly while charging. Your charge attack is resolved normally. On a successful hit, you deal an extra 5d6 points of fire damage to the target of your charge.

This maneuver is a supernatural ability.
